  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242976.htm", 
  "description": "<p>对于微软来说，刚刚发布的Windows 8.1系统是重新挽回颜面的重要工具，它改进了很多Windows 8系统中令人崩溃的设计，比如恢复了开始按钮等。当然，Windows 8.1的改进更多是细节而不是革命，因为归根结底它只是一个更新，而不是一个全新的操作系统。<strong>虽然我们之前为大家详解了Windows 8.1新的应用程序和隐藏功能，但在试用了Windows 8.1预览版一天之后，我们仍然发现很多不完美之处，下面就为大家总结出Windows 8.1遗漏的12项功能更新，看看你是否也感同身受。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e02ccb6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242976.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E9%81%97%E6%BC%8F%E7%9A%8412%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242976.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E9%81%97%E6%BC%8F%E7%9A%8412%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242976.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E9%81%97%E6%BC%8F%E7%9A%8412%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242976.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E9%81%97%E6%BC%8F%E7%9A%8412%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242976.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E9%81%97%E6%BC%8F%E7%9A%8412%E9%A1%B9%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td>