  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242975.htm", 
  "description": "<p>传了许久的红米手机显得颇为神秘，之前红米1代通过了入网许可证，不过后来它的牌照被撤销了，随后有消息人士透露，红米1没有通过中国移动的入库测试。即使这样，小米似乎也没有放弃打造支持TD网络的小米手机，于是乎红米2代就浮出了水面，而之前的消息显示，这款手机会与小米3于8月16日同步发布。现在有<a class=\"f14_link\" href=\"http://weibo.com/tdzhijia?from=profile&#38;wvr=5&#38;loc=tagweibo\" target=\"_blank\">网友</a>率先放出了红米2代的ROM，<strong>其代码显示该机搭载的是MT6589四核处理器，同时内置了如支付宝、亚马逊、WPS等等常用应用，而且默认壁纸也与小米系机器内置的一样。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e02ccb3/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242975.htm&amp;t=999%E5%85%83%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%BA%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242975.htm&amp;t=999%E5%85%83%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%BA%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242975.htm&amp;t=999%E5%85%83%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%BA%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242975.htm&amp;t=999%E5%85%83%EF%BC%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A5%9E%E7%A7%98%E5%9B%9B%E6%A0%B8%E6%9C%BA%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%